Package: suitr
Type: Package
Title: This Package Makes It Easy to Create Cards in R Either for Printing in 
  The Console or for Html Export
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gregor de Cillia
Authors@R: c(person("Gregor", "de Cillia", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "de.cillia.gregor@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Gregor de Cillia <de.cillia.gregor@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of converter functions to obtain the unicode representation
  of playing cards, chess pieces and more. The resulting strigs can also converted
  into browsable html objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: magrittr, htmltools
Suggests: crayon
URL: https://www.github.com/GregorDeCillia/suitr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
